@Haxley17 1899 I vote #RM for #ArtistaAsiatico at #SECAwards

These posts use the Distract tactic by including irrelevant information or changing the topic. In the first example, the mention of "Marcos" is not related to the voting for #RM for #ArtistaAsiatico at #SECAwards. In the second example, the number "1899" is also not relevant to the voting at #SECAwards. This tactic can sometimes be used to confuse or mislead others or simply as a way to disrupt the flow of conversation.
